Refactor NRCISYF scenarios using shared modernised framework; add @Before hook 
for CISYF-specific data resolution; implement 15-attempt herd loop with 
escalating DB limit (start 10, +5 per retry); test across all farming entity 
types and category combinations; remove PII from comments; integrate with main 
nightly schedule.

